gn:left\'><b><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\'>发件人<span lang=EN-US>:</span></span></b><span\r\nlang=EN-US style=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\'> </span><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\'>曾少桃<span lang=EN-US> <br>\r\n</span><b>发送时间<span lang=EN-US>:</span></b><span lang=EN-US> 2014</span>年<span\r\nlang=EN-US>6</span>月<span lang=EN-US>3</span>日<span lang=EN-US> 11:07<br>\r\n</span><b>收件人<span lang=EN-US>:</span></b><span lang=EN-US> ^</span>各部门信息员<span\r\nlang=EN-US>; ^</span>工会小组长<span lang=EN-US><br>\r\n</span><b>抄送<span lang=EN-US>:</span></b><span lang=EN-US> %</span>人力资源中心所有人<span\r\nlang=EN-US><br>\r\n</span><b>主题<span lang=EN-US>:</span></b><span lang=EN-US> 2014</span>年度员工旅游费发放通知<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=left style=\'text-align:left\'><span lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=\'text-align:center;layout-grid-mode:char\'><span\r\nlang=EN-US style=\'font-size:18.0pt;font-family:隶书\'>2014</span><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:18.0pt;font-family:宋体\'>年度员工旅游费发放通知</span><span lang=EN-US\r\nstyle=\'font-size:18.0pt;font-family:隶书\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style=\'text-align:center;layout-grid-mode:char\'><span\r\nlang=EN-US style=\'font-size:18.0pt;font-family:隶书\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-indent:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\'><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>为加强公司员工的团体协作精神，增加员工间彼此的了解及沟通，有效提升公司团队的执行力和凝聚力；同时为丰富员工的业余文化生活，陶治情操，缓解员工工作压力，让员工在工作之余享受大自然的怡人风光，并体现公司对员工的关怀，树立公司人性化管理典范。员工旅游费发放通知如下：<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>一、</span></span><![endif]><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>发放旅游费对象：<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>1、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:宋体\'>2012</span><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>年<span lang=EN-US>12</span>月<span lang=EN-US>31</span>日前入厂的员工每人发放<span\r\nlang=EN-US>120</span>元。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>2、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:宋体\'>2013</span><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>年<span lang=EN-US>1</span>月<span lang=EN-US>1</span>日至<span\r\nlang=EN-US>2013</span>年<span lang=EN-US>12</span>月<span lang=EN-US>31</span>日入厂的员工每人发放<span\r\nlang=EN-US>60</span>元。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>3、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>外借人员的旅游费由所在单位自行解决。<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>4、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:宋体\'>2014</span><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>年新入厂的大中专生不发放旅游费，另行由人力资源中心组织团体旅游活动（旅游费用按<span lang=EN-US>120</span>元<span\r\nlang=EN-US>/</span>每人计算）。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>二、</span></span><![endif]><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>发放旅游费办法：<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>1、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>各部门、车间的旅游费用由工会小组长负责管理。<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>2、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>组织旅游前一周工会小组长须提交《<span\r\nlang=EN-US>2014</span>年员工旅游费统计表》、变动表及报团人员名单表到人力资源中心审核审批后再到财务部报账；员工须在《<span\r\nlang=EN-US>2014</span>年员工旅游费统计表》上亲笔签名签收，报团人员名单表须盖旅游公司公章。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>3、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>如有特殊情况不能参加集体旅游者，经所在部门经理或车间主管同意，可发放其本人应发旅游费金额的<span\r\nlang=EN-US>50%</span>自行旅游。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>三、</span></span><![endif]><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>旅游程序：<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>1、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>车间旅游先将旅游人员名单、时间、地点报生产部、<span\r\nlang=EN-US>PMC</span>、人力资源中心、安委及事业部或中心总经理审批后，才能外出旅游；（即<span lang=EN-US>OA&nbsp;\r\n</span>车间旅游申请流程）<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>2、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>部门旅游先将旅游人员名单、时间、地点报人力资源中心、安委及事业部或中心总经理审批后，才能外出旅游。（即<span\r\nlang=EN-US>OA&nbsp; </span>部门旅游申请流程）<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>四、</span></span><![endif]><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'>旅游假期处理：<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo4;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char\'><![if !supportLists]><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>1、<span style=\'font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>原则上<span\r\nlang=EN-US>2014</span>年新分配大学生，统一由人力资源中心组织团体旅游活动，如实习期间参加部门、车间旅游活动，需提前三天书面申请经所在实习部门经理或车间主管同意后交人力资源中心审批。旅游假期均按事假处理，旅游费用自理。<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\'><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:宋体\'>2</span><span style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'>、<span style=\'color:blue\'>凡参加部门、车间集体旅游活动的人员并符合旅游费发放条件，公司给予<span lang=EN-US>1</span>天公假旅游（每人在<span\r\nlang=EN-US>2014</span>年度只能享受<span lang=EN-US>1</span>天公假旅游，），人力资源中心按报团名单表进行审核（经旅游公司盖公章），当旅游假期＞<span\r\nlang=EN-US>1</span>天的可使用调休假及年休假期或事假。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:15.75pt;text-indent:-15.75pt;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\'><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-family:宋体\'>3</span><span style=\'font-family:\r\n宋体\'>、<span style=\'color:blue\'>自行旅游者不享受公司<span lang=EN-US>1</span>天公假旅游待遇。</span><span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'layout-grid-mode:char\'><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>五、旅游费报帐截止日期：<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-indent:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\'><span\r\nlang=EN-US style=\'font-family:宋体\'>2014</span><span style=\'font-family:宋体\'>年员工旅游费报帐截止日期为<span\r\nlang=EN-US>2014</span>年<span lang=EN-US>12</span>月<span lang=EN-US>25</span>日。<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\'><b><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:fuchsia\'>旅游费明细表已放在<span\r\nlang=EN-US>OA</span>系统――人力资源门户――旅游<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\'><b><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:\"微软雅黑\",\"sans-serif\";color:#2403E7\'>人力资源中心目标：以人为本，促进企业与员工共同发展；<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\'><b><span\r\nstyle=\'font-family:\"微软雅黑\",\"sans-serif\";color:#2403E7\'>人力资源中心使命：打造最优秀的人力资源团队，实施百年国光的人才战略<span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\'><span\r\nstyle=\'font-size:13.5pt;font-family:隶书\'>人力资源中心：曾少桃</span><span lang=EN-US\r\nstyle=\'font-family:宋体\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:13.5pt;font-family:隶书\'>内线：<span\r\nlang=EN-US>5173</span>（外线<span lang=EN-US>020-28605173</span>）</span><span\r\nlang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:13.5pt;font-family:隶书\'>短号：<span\r\nlang=EN-US>668285</span></span><span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:10.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>\r\n', null, 'yangyan@ggec.gd', '杨雁', '1', '1', '', '', '%信息部所有人<^5@ggec.gd>', '196', 'o7Chyt0jbuYPa5AWGDQ-Ttbk2gGU', '2014-06-03 11:21:17', '0', '2014-06-03 11:21:15', '2', '转发: 2014年度员工旅游费发放通知', 'lzr@ggec.gd');
